title: GoPro HD: Dogs of the Teva Mountain Games 2012
description:
Shot 100% on the HD HERO2® camera 

It's time for PUPPIES!!!! Check out the dogs of the TEVA Mountain Games 2012. They walk, they skate, they jump - they're sooooo fluffy!

A big thanks to Kendall and Aaron Chase, as well as to all the cute puppies, doggies and owners!

Music
BLACKBIRD BLACKBIRD "Give You Everything"
